Package foundation.omni.rpc.test

Class OmniTestClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.consensusj.jsonrpc.AbstractRpcClient
      • org.consensusj.jsonrpc.RpcClient
        • com.msgilligan.bitcoinj.rpc.BitcoinClient
          • com.msgilligan.bitcoinj.rpc.BitcoinExtendedClient
            • foundation.omni.rpc.OmniClient
              • foundation.omni.rpc.test.OmniTestClient
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NetworkParametersProperty, DynamicRpcMethodSupport
    public class OmniTestClient
extends OmniClient
    OmniClient subclass that adds methods to create raw Omni transactions and send them using "omniSendRawTx". This avoids error-checking on the RPCs and allows us to test the effect of sending raw transactions that would be disallowed by this checking. It is essentially a clone of the deprecated OmniExtendedClient with a name and package that indicates it is for testing purposes.
